    "text": "This key translates the label \"Input tokens,\" which appears next to an icon in the pricing card of an AI service. It describes the tokens consumed by the AI service and is displayed within the Portal Settings > Payments > SaaS > Services section. Translators should ensure the translation accurately reflects the technical meaning of \"input tokens\" in this context.",
